<hgroup><h1>Patient Trajectories Among Persons Hospitalized for COVID-19</h1>
<p>A Cohort Study</p></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Garibaldi%20BT"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Brian T Garibaldi</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
